Program Flow Description
1. Show Menu
The program repeatedly shows this menu:

Write a new entry

Display journal

Save journal

Load journal

Quit

2. Write a New Entry
Program asks PromptGenerator for a random prompt

Displays the prompt to the user

User types their response

Program gets the current date

Creates a new Entry object

Adds it to the Journal

3. Display Journal
Program calls Journal.DisplayAll()

Each Entry prints itself

4. Save Journal
Program asks for a filename

Calls Journal.SaveToFile(filename)

Journal writes each Entry to the file

5. Load Journal
Program asks for a filename

Calls Journal.LoadFromFile(filename)

Journal replaces its entries with the ones from the file